<div type="definition">
<p>BIG as NOISE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. There is no word dedicated to the loudness of sound, the current way of expressing this meaning is to use dà 大 "large".</p>
